                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100606-44-off242 t18100606-44-cd243"></join>, a handkerchief, value 4 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18100606-44-victim417" type="victimName">
                           David 
